msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.27"
msgid "Evampi bhoto rañño vattā dhammato natthi. "
msgstr "Those who speak against the king in this way have no legitimacy. "

msgctxt "dn5:17.28"
msgid "Bhavaṃ kho pana rājā paṇḍito viyatto medhāvī paṭibalo atītānāgatapaccuppanne atthe cintetuṃ. "
msgstr "For the king does indeed possess the eight factors. "

msgctxt "dn5:17.29"
msgid "Imināpetaṃ bhavaṃ rājā jānātu, yajataṃ bhavaṃ, sajjataṃ bhavaṃ, modataṃ bhavaṃ, cittameva bhavaṃ antaraṃ pasādetu. (6–12.) "
msgstr "Let the king know this too as a reason to sacrifice, relinquish, rejoice, and gain confidence in his heart. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.141, sc67
msgctxt "dn5:17.30"
msgid "Siyā kho pana bhoto rañño mahāyaññaṃ yajamānassa kocideva vattā: "
msgstr "While the king is performing the great sacrifice, someone might say "

msgctxt "dn5:17.31"
msgid "‘rājā kho mahāvijito mahāyaññaṃ yajati. "
msgstr "that the high priest does not possess the four factors. "

msgctxt "dn5:17.32"
msgid "No ca khvassa purohito brāhmaṇo ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena; "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.33"
msgid "atha ca pana bhavaṃ rājā evarūpaṃ mahāyaññaṃ yajatī’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.34"
msgid "Evampi bhoto rañño vattā dhammato natthi. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.35"
msgid "Bhoto kho pana rañño purohito brāhmaṇo ubhato sujāto mātito ca pitito ca saṃsuddhagahaṇiko yāva sattamā pitāmahayugā akkhitto anupakkuṭṭho jātivādena. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.36"
msgid "Imināpetaṃ bhavaṃ rājā jānātu, yajataṃ bhavaṃ, sajjataṃ bhavaṃ, modataṃ bhavaṃ, cittameva bhavaṃ antaraṃ pasādetu. (13) "
msgstr " "

#. REF: sc68
msgctxt "dn5:17.37"
msgid "Siyā kho pana bhoto rañño mahāyaññaṃ yajamānassa kocideva vattā: "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.38"
msgid "‘rājā kho mahāvijito mahāyaññaṃ yajati. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.39"
msgid "No ca khvassa purohito brāhmaṇo ajjhāyako mantadharo tiṇṇaṃ vedānaṃ pāragū sanighaṇḍukeṭubhānaṃ sākkharappabhedānaṃ itihāsapañcamānaṃ padako veyyākaraṇo lokāyatamahāpurisalakkhaṇesu anavayo … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.40"
msgid "no ca khvassa purohito brāhmaṇo sīlavā vuddhasīlī vuddhasīlena samannāgato … pe … "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.41"
msgid "no ca khvassa purohito brāhmaṇo paṇḍito viyatto medhāvī paṭhamo vā dutiyo vā sujaṃ paggaṇhantānaṃ, atha ca pana bhavaṃ rājā evarūpaṃ mahāyaññaṃ yajatī’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "dn5:17.42"
msgid "Evampi bhoto rañño vattā dhammato natthi. "
msgstr "Those who speak against the king in this way have no legitimacy. "

msgctxt "dn5:17.43"
msgid "Bhoto kho pana rañño purohito brāhmaṇo paṇḍito viyatto medhāvī paṭhamo vā dutiyo vā sujaṃ paggaṇhantānaṃ. "
msgstr "For the high priest does indeed possess the four factors. "

msgctxt "dn5:17.44"
msgid "Imināpetaṃ bhavaṃ rājā jānātu, yajataṃ bhavaṃ, sajjataṃ bhavaṃ, modataṃ bhavaṃ, cittameva bhavaṃ antaraṃ pasādetūti. "
msgstr "Let the king know this too as a reason to sacrifice, relinquish, rejoice, and gain confidence in his heart.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:17.45"
msgid "Imehi kho, brāhmaṇa, purohito brāhmaṇo rañño mahāvijitassa mahāyaññaṃ yajamānassa soḷasahi ākārehi cittaṃ sandassesi samādapesi samuttejesi sampahaṃsesi. (14–16.) "
msgstr "These are the sixteen respects in which the high priest educated, encouraged, fired up, and inspired the king’s mind while he was performing the sacrifice. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs18, sc69
#. VAR: barihisatthāya → pari­hiṃ­satthāya (si, s1-3, mr) | para­hiṃ­satthāya (mr)
msgctxt "dn5:18.1"
msgid "Tasmiṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yaññe neva gāvo haññiṃsu, na ajeḷakā haññiṃsu, na kukkuṭasūkarā haññiṃsu, na vividhā pāṇā saṅghātaṃ āpajjiṃsu, na rukkhā chijjiṃsu yūpatthāya, na dabbhā lūyiṃsu barihisatthāya. "
msgstr "And brahmin, in that sacrifice no cattle were killed, no goats were killed, and no chickens or pigs were killed. There was no slaughter of various kinds of creatures. No trees were felled for the sacrificial post. No grass was reaped to strew over the place of sacrifice. "

msgctxt "dn5:18.2"
msgid "Yepissa ahesuṃ dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, tepi na daṇḍatajjitā na bhayatajjitā na assumukhā rudamānā parikammāni akaṃsu. "
msgstr "No bondservants, employees, or workers did their jobs under threat of punishment and danger, weeping with tearful faces. "

msgctxt "dn5:18.3"
msgid "Atha kho ye icchiṃsu, te akaṃsu, ye na icchiṃsu, na te akaṃsu; "
msgstr "Those who wished to work did so, while those who did not wish to did not. "

msgctxt "dn5:18.4"
msgid "yaṃ icchiṃsu, taṃ akaṃsu, yaṃ na icchiṃsu, na taṃ akaṃsu. "
msgstr "They did the work they wanted to, and did not do what they didn’t want to. "

msgctxt "dn5:18.5"
msgid "Sappitelanavanītadadhimadhuphāṇitena ceva so yañño niṭṭhānamagamāsi. "
msgstr "The sacrifice was completed with just ghee, oil, butter, curds, honey, and molasses. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs19, pts-vp-pli1.142, sc70
msgctxt "dn5:19.1"
msgid "Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, khattiyā ānuyantā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, amaccā pārisajjā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, brāhmaṇamahāsālā negamā ceva jānapadā ca, gahapatinecayikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ ādāya rājānaṃ mahāvijitaṃ upasaṅkamitvā evamāhaṃsu: "
msgstr "Then the aristocrat vassals, ministers and counselors, well-to-do brahmins, and well-off householders of both town and country came to the king bringing abundant wealth and said, "

# NOTE: RD’s translation of this passage is more accurate than MW’s.
msgctxt "dn5:19.2"
msgid "‘idaṃ, deva, pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ devaññeva uddissābhataṃ, taṃ devo paṭiggaṇhātū’ti. "
msgstr "‘Sire, this abundant wealth is specially for you alone; may Your Highness accept it!’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:19.3"
msgid "‘Alaṃ, bho, mamāpidaṃ pahūtaṃ sāpateyyaṃ dhammikena balinā abhisaṅkhataṃ; "
msgstr "‘There’s enough raised for me through regular taxes. Let this be for you; and here, take even more!’ "

msgctxt "dn5:19.4"
msgid "tañca vo hotu, ito ca bhiyyo harathā’ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:19.5"
msgid "Te raññā paṭikkhittā ekamantaṃ apakkamma evaṃ samacintesuṃ: "
msgstr "When the king turned them down, they withdrew to one side to think up a plan, "

msgctxt "dn5:19.6"
msgid "‘na kho etaṃ amhākaṃ patirūpaṃ, yaṃ mayaṃ imāni sāpateyyāni punadeva sakāni gharāni paṭihareyyāma. "
msgstr "‘It wouldn’t be proper for us to take this abundant wealth back to our own homes. "

msgctxt "dn5:19.7"
msgid "Rājā kho mahāvijito mahāyaññaṃ yajati, handassa mayaṃ anuyāgino homā’ti. "
msgstr "King Mahāvijita is performing a great sacrifice. Let us make an offering as an auxiliary sacrifice.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs20, sc71
#. VAR: yaññavāṭassa → yaññāvāṭassa (bj, pts1, mr) | yaññavātassa (s1-3)
msgctxt "dn5:20.1"
msgid "Atha kho, brāhmaṇa, puratthimena yaññavāṭassa khattiyā ānuyantā negamā ceva jānapadā ca dānāni paṭṭhapesuṃ. "
msgstr "Then the aristocrat vassals of town and country set up gifts to the east of the sacrificial pit. "

msgctxt "dn5:20.2"
msgid "Dakkhiṇena yaññavāṭassa amaccā pārisajjā negamā ceva jānapadā ca dānāni paṭṭhapesuṃ. "
msgstr "The ministers and counselors of town and country set up gifts to the south of the sacrificial pit. "

msgctxt "dn5:20.3"
msgid "Pacchimena yaññavāṭassa brāhmaṇamahāsālā negamā ceva jānapadā ca dānāni paṭṭhapesuṃ. "
msgstr "The well-to-do brahmins of town and country set up gifts to the west of the sacrificial pit. "

msgctxt "dn5:20.4"
msgid "Uttarena yaññavāṭassa gahapatinecayikā negamā ceva jānapadā ca dānāni paṭṭhapesuṃ. "
msgstr "The well-off householders of town and country set up gifts to the north of the sacrificial pit. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc72
msgctxt "dn5:20.5"
msgid "Tesupi kho, brāhmaṇa, yaññesu neva gāvo haññiṃsu, na ajeḷakā haññiṃsu, na kukkuṭasūkarā haññiṃsu, na vividhā pāṇā saṅghātaṃ āpajjiṃsu, na rukkhā chijjiṃsu yūpatthāya, na dabbhā lūyiṃsu barihisatthāya. "
msgstr "And brahmin, in that sacrifice too no cattle were killed, no goats were killed, and no chickens or pigs were killed. There was no slaughter of various kinds of creatures. No trees were felled for the sacrificial post. No grass was reaped to strew over the place of sacrifice. "

msgctxt "dn5:20.6"
msgid "Yepi nesaṃ ahesuṃ dāsāti vā pessāti vā kammakarāti vā, tepi na daṇḍatajjitā na bhayatajjitā na assumukhā rudamānā parikammāni akaṃsu. "
msgstr "No bondservants, employees, or workers did their jobs under threat of punishment and danger, weeping with tearful faces. "

msgctxt "dn5:20.7"
msgid "Atha kho ye icchiṃsu, te akaṃsu, ye na icchiṃsu, na te akaṃsu; "
msgstr "Those who wished to work did so, while those who did not wish to did not. "

msgctxt "dn5:20.8"
msgid "yaṃ icchiṃsu, taṃ akaṃsu, yaṃ na icchiṃsu na taṃ akaṃsu. "
msgstr "They did the work they wanted to, and did not do what they didn’t want to. "

msgctxt "dn5:20.9"
msgid "Sappitelanavanītadadhimadhuphāṇitena ceva te yaññā niṭṭhānamagamaṃsu. "
msgstr "The sacrifice was completed with just ghee, oil, butter, curds, honey, and molasses. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.143, sc73
msgctxt "dn5:20.10"
msgid "Iti cattāro ca anumatipakkhā, rājā mahāvijito aṭṭhahaṅgehi samannāgato, purohito brāhmaṇo catūhaṅgehi samannāgato; "
msgstr "And so there were four consenting factions, eight factors possessed by King Mahāvijita, four factors possessed by the high priest, "

msgctxt "dn5:20.11"
msgid "tisso ca vidhā. "
msgstr "and three modes. "

msgctxt "dn5:20.12"
msgid "Ayaṃ vuccati, brāhmaṇa, tividhā yaññasampadā soḷasaparikkhārā”ti. "
msgstr "Brahmin, this is called the sacrifice accomplished with three modes and sixteen accessories.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs21, sc74
msgctxt "dn5:21.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, te brāhmaṇā unnādino uccāsaddamahāsaddā ahesuṃ: "
msgstr "When he said this, those brahmins made an uproar, "

msgctxt "dn5:21.2"
msgid "“aho yañño, aho yaññasampadā”ti. "
msgstr "“Hooray for such sacrifice! Hooray for the accomplishment of such sacrifice!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:21.3"
msgid "Kūṭadanto pana brāhmaṇo tūṇhībhūtova nisinno hoti. "
msgstr "But the brahmin Kūṭadanta sat in silence. "

msgctxt "dn5:21.4"
msgid "Atha kho te brāhmaṇā kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ etadavocuṃ: "
msgstr "So those brahmins said to him, "

msgctxt "dn5:21.5"
msgid "“kasmā pana bhavaṃ kūṭadanto samaṇassa gotamassa subhāsitaṃ subhāsitato nābbhanumodatī”ti? "
msgstr "“How can you not applaud the ascetic Gotama’s fine words?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:21.6"
msgid "“Nāhaṃ, bho, samaṇassa gotamassa subhāsitaṃ subhāsitato nābbhanumodāmi. "
msgstr "“It’s not that I don’t applaud what he said. "

msgctxt "dn5:21.7"
msgid "Muddhāpi tassa vipateyya, yo samaṇassa gotamassa subhāsitaṃ subhāsitato nābbhanumodeyya. "
msgstr "If anyone didn’t applaud such fine words, their head would explode! "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:21.8"
msgid "Api ca me, bho, evaṃ hoti—"
msgstr "But, gentlemen, it occurs to me that "

msgctxt "dn5:21.9"
msgid "samaṇo gotamo na evamāha: "
msgstr "the ascetic Gotama does not say: "

msgctxt "dn5:21.10"
msgid "‘evaṃ me sutan’ti vā ‘evaṃ arahati bhavitun’ti vā; "
msgstr "‘So I have heard’ or ‘It ought to be like this.’ "

msgctxt "dn5:21.11"
msgid "api ca samaṇo gotamo: "
msgstr "Rather, he just says: "

msgctxt "dn5:21.12"
msgid "‘evaṃ tadā āsi, itthaṃ tadā āsi’ tveva bhāsati. "
msgstr "‘So it was then, this is how it was then.’ "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:21.13"
msgid "Tassa mayhaṃ bho evaṃ hoti: "
msgstr "It occurs to me that "

msgctxt "dn5:21.14"
msgid "‘addhā samaṇo gotamo tena samayena rājā vā ahosi mahāvijito yaññassāmi purohito vā brāhmaṇo tassa yaññassa yājetā’ti. "
msgstr "the ascetic Gotama at that time must have been King Mahāvijita, the owner of the sacrifice, or else the brahmin high priest who facilitated the sacrifice for him. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:21.15"
msgid "Abhijānāti pana bhavaṃ gotamo evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ yajitvā vā yājetvā vā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjitā”ti? "
msgstr "Does Master Gotama recall having performed such a sacrifice, or having facilitated it, and then, when his body broke up, after death, being reborn in a good place, a heavenly realm?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:21.16"
msgid "“Abhijānāmahaṃ, brāhmaṇa, evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ yajitvā vā yājetvā vā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjitā, ahaṃ tena samayena purohito brāhmaṇo ahosiṃ tassa yaññassa yājetā”ti. "
msgstr "“I do recall that, brahmin. For at that time I was the brahmin high priest who facilitated the sacrifice.” "

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:21.17"
msgid "5. Niccadānaanukulayañña "
msgstr "5. A Regular Gift as an Ongoing Family Sacrifice. "

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: pts-cs22, sc75
#. VAR: appaṭṭhataro → appatthataro (s1-3, km)
#. VAR: tividhāya yaññasampadāya → tividha­yañña­sam­padāya (mr)
msgctxt "dn5:22.1"
msgid "“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "“But Master Gotama, apart from that sacrifice accomplished with three modes and sixteen accessories, is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.144, sc76
msgctxt "dn5:22.2"
msgid "“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr "“There is, brahmin.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc77
msgctxt "dn5:22.3"
msgid "“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "“But what is it?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc78
msgctxt "dn5:22.4"
msgid "“Yāni kho pana tāni, brāhmaṇa, niccadānāni anukulayaññāni sīlavante pabbajite uddissa diyyanti; "
msgstr "“The regular gifts as ongoing family sacrifice given specially to ethical renunciates; "

msgctxt "dn5:22.5"
msgid "ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr "this sacrifice, brahmin, has fewer requirements and undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs23, sc79
msgctxt "dn5:23.1"
msgid "“Ko nu kho, bho gotama, hetu ko paccayo, yena taṃ niccadānaṃ anukulayaññaṃ imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhatarañca appasamārambhatarañca mahapphalatarañca mahānisaṃsatarañcā”ti? "
msgstr "“What is the cause, Master Gotama, what is the reason why those regular gifts as ongoing family sacrifice have fewer requirements and undertakings, yet are more fruitful and beneficial, compared with the sacrifice accomplished with three modes and sixteen accessories?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc80
msgctxt "dn5:23.2"
msgid "“Na kho, brāhmaṇa, evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ upasaṅkamanti arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannā. "
msgstr "“Because neither perfected ones nor those who have entered the path to perfection will attend such a sacrifice. "

msgctxt "dn5:23.3"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "dn5:23.4"
msgid "Dissanti hettha, brāhmaṇa, daṇḍappahārāpi galaggahāpi, tasmā evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ na upasaṅkamanti arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannā. "
msgstr "Because beatings and throttlings are seen there. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:23.5"
msgid "Yāni kho pana tāni, brāhmaṇa, niccadānāni anukulayaññāni sīlavante pabbajite uddissa diyyanti; "
msgstr "But the regular gifts as ongoing family sacrifice given specially to ethical renunciates; "

msgctxt "dn5:23.6"
msgid "evarūpaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yaññaṃ upasaṅkamanti arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannā. "
msgstr "perfected ones and those who have entered the path to perfection will attend such a sacrifice. "

msgctxt "dn5:23.7"
msgid "Taṃ kissa hetu? "
msgstr "Why is that? "

msgctxt "dn5:23.8"
msgid "Na hettha, brāhmaṇa, dissanti daṇḍappahārāpi galaggahāpi, tasmā evarūpaṃ yaññaṃ upasaṅkamanti arahanto vā arahattamaggaṃ vā samāpannā. "
msgstr "Because no beatings and throttlings are seen there. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:23.9"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, hetu ayaṃ paccayo, yena taṃ niccadānaṃ anukulayaññaṃ imāya tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya appaṭṭhatarañca appasamārambhatarañca mahapphalatarañca mahānisaṃsatarañcā”ti. "
msgstr "This is the cause, brahmin, this is the reason why those regular gifts as ongoing family sacrifice have fewer requirements and undertakings, yet are more fruitful and beneficial, compared with the sacrifice accomplished with three modes and sixteen accessories.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs24, pts-vp-pli1.145, sc81
msgctxt "dn5:24.1"
msgid "“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "“But Master Gotama, apart from that sacrifice accomplished with three modes and sixteen accessories and those regular gifts as ongoing family sacrifice, is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc82
msgctxt "dn5:24.2"
msgid "“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr "“There is, brahmin.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc83
msgctxt "dn5:24.3"
msgid "“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "“But what is it?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc84
msgctxt "dn5:24.4"
msgid "“Yo kho, brāhmaṇa, cātuddisaṃ saṅghaṃ uddissa vihāraṃ karoti, ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr "“When someone gives a dwelling specially for the Saṅgha of the four quarters.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs25, sc85
msgctxt "dn5:25.1"
msgid "“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "“But is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc86
msgctxt "dn5:25.2"
msgid "“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc87
msgctxt "dn5:25.3"
msgid "“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.146, sc88
msgctxt "dn5:25.4"
msgid "“Yo kho, brāhmaṇa, pasannacitto buddhaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati, dhammaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati, saṅghaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchati; "
msgstr "“When someone with confident heart goes for refuge to the Buddha, the teaching, and the Saṅgha.” "

msgctxt "dn5:25.5"
msgid "ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs26, sc89
msgctxt "dn5:26.1"
msgid "“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena imehi ca saraṇagamanehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "“But is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc90
msgctxt "dn5:26.2"
msgid "“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena imehi ca saraṇagamanehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc91
msgctxt "dn5:26.3"
msgid "“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena imehi ca saraṇagamanehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc92
msgctxt "dn5:26.4"
msgid "“Yo kho, brāhmaṇa, pasannacitto sikkhāpadāni samādiyati—"
msgstr "“When someone with a confident heart undertakes the training rules "

msgctxt "dn5:26.5"
msgid "pāṇātipātā veramaṇiṃ, adinnādānā veramaṇiṃ, kāmesumicchācārā veramaṇiṃ, musāvādā veramaṇiṃ, surāmerayamajjapamādaṭṭhānā veramaṇiṃ. "
msgstr "to refrain from killing living creatures, stealing, sexual misconduct, lying, and alcoholic drinks that cause negligence.” "

msgctxt "dn5:26.6"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena imehi ca saraṇagamanehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs27, sc93
msgctxt "dn5:27.1"
msgid "“Atthi pana, bho gotama, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena imehi ca saraṇagamanehi imehi ca sikkhāpadehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr "“But is there any other sacrifice that has fewer requirements and undertakings, yet is more fruitful and beneficial?” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc94
msgctxt "dn5:27.2"
msgid "“Atthi kho, brāhmaṇa, añño yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena imehi ca saraṇagamanehi imehi ca sikkhāpadehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti. "
msgstr "“There is, brahmin. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.147, sc95
msgctxt "dn5:27.3"
msgid "“Katamo pana so, bho gotama, yañño imāya ca tividhāya yaññasampadāya soḷasaparikkhārāya iminā ca niccadānena anukulayaññena iminā ca vihāradānena imehi ca saraṇagamanehi imehi ca sikkhāpadehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cā”ti? "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc96
msgctxt "dn5:27.4"
msgid "“Idha, brāhmaṇa, tathāgato loke uppajjati arahaṃ sammāsambuddho … pe … "
msgstr "It’s when a Realized One arises in the world, perfected, a fully awakened Buddha … "

msgctxt "dn5:27.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, bhikkhu sīlasampanno hoti … pe … "
msgstr "That’s how a mendicant is accomplished in ethics. … "

msgctxt "dn5:27.6"
msgid "paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "They enter and remain in the first absorption … "

msgctxt "dn5:27.7"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño purimehi yaññehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro ca … pe … "
msgstr "This sacrifice has fewer requirements and undertakings than the former, yet is more fruitful and beneficial. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc97
msgctxt "dn5:27.8"
msgid "Dutiyaṃ jhānaṃ … "
msgstr "They enter and remain in the second absorption … "

msgctxt "dn5:27.9"
msgid "tatiyaṃ jhānaṃ … "
msgstr "third absorption … "

msgctxt "dn5:27.10"
msgid "catutthaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja viharati. "
msgstr "fourth absorption. "

msgctxt "dn5:27.11"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño purimehi yaññehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro cāti. … pe … "
msgstr "This sacrifice has fewer requirements and undertakings than the former, yet is more fruitful and beneficial. … "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:27.12"
msgid "Ñāṇadassanāya cittaṃ abhinīharati abhininnāmeti … "
msgstr "They extend and project the mind toward knowledge and vision … "

msgctxt "dn5:27.13"
msgid "ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño purimehi yaññehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro ca … pe … "
msgstr "This sacrifice has fewer requirements and undertakings than the former, yet is more fruitful and beneficial. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:27.14"
msgid "nāparaṃ itthattāyāti pajānāti. "
msgstr "They understand: ‘… there is no return to any state of existence.’ "

msgctxt "dn5:27.15"
msgid "Ayampi kho, brāhmaṇa, yañño purimehi yaññehi appaṭṭhataro ca appasamārambhataro ca mahapphalataro ca mahānisaṃsataro ca. "
msgstr "This sacrifice has fewer requirements and undertakings than the former, yet is more fruitful and beneficial. "

msgctxt "dn5:27.16"
msgid "Imāya ca, brāhmaṇa, yaññasampadāya aññā yaññasampadā uttaritarā vā paṇītatarā vā natthī”ti. "
msgstr "And, brahmin, there is no other accomplishment of sacrifice which is better and finer than this.” "

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:27.17"
msgid "6. Kūṭadantaupāsakattapaṭivedanā "
msgstr "6. Kūṭadanta Declares Himself a Lay Follower "

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: pts-cs28, pts-vp-pli1.148, sc98
msgctxt "dn5:28.1"
msgid "Evaṃ vutte, kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "When he had spoken, Kūṭadanta said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "dn5:28.2"
msgid "“abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama, abhikkantaṃ, bho gotama. "
msgstr "“Excellent, Master Gotama! Excellent! "

msgctxt "dn5:28.3"
msgid "Seyyathāpi, bho gotama, nikkujjitaṃ vā ukkujjeyya, paṭicchannaṃ vā vivareyya, mūḷhassa vā maggaṃ ācikkheyya, andhakāre vā telapajjotaṃ dhāreyya: ‘cakkhumanto rūpāni dakkhantī’ti; evamevaṃ bhotā gotamena anekapariyāyena dhammo pakāsito. "
msgstr "As if he were righting the overturned, or revealing the hidden, or pointing out the path to the lost, or lighting a lamp in the dark so people with good eyes can see what’s there, Master Gotama has made the Teaching clear in many ways. "

msgctxt "dn5:28.4"
msgid "Esāhaṃ bhavantaṃ gotamaṃ saraṇaṃ gacchāmi dhammañca bhikkhusaṅghañca. "
msgstr "I go for refuge to Master Gotama, to the teaching, and to the mendicant Saṅgha. "

msgctxt "dn5:28.5"
msgid "Upāsakaṃ maṃ bhavaṃ gotamo dhāretu ajjatagge pāṇupetaṃ saraṇaṃ gataṃ. "
msgstr "From this day forth, may Master Gotama remember me as a lay follower who has gone for refuge for life. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "dn5:28.6"
msgid "Esāhaṃ, bho gotama, satta ca usabhasatāni satta ca vacchatarasatāni satta ca vacchatarīsatāni satta ca ajasatāni satta ca urabbhasatāni muñcāmi, jīvitaṃ demi, haritāni ceva tiṇāni khādantu, sītāni ca pānīyāni pivantu, sīto ca nesaṃ vāto upavāyatū”ti. "
msgstr "And these bulls, bullocks, heifers, goats, and rams—seven hundred of each—I release them, I grant them life! Let them eat green grass and drink cool water, and may a cool breeze blow upon them!” "

#. HTML: </p><h2>
msgctxt "dn5:28.7"
msgid "7. Sotāpattiphalasacchikiriyā "
msgstr "7. The Realization of the Fruit of Stream-Entry "

#. HTML: </h2><p>
#. REF: pts-cs29, sc99
msgctxt "dn5:29.1"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa anupubbiṃ kathaṃ kathesi, "
msgstr "Then the Buddha taught Kūṭadanta step by step, with "

msgctxt "dn5:29.2"
msgid "seyyathidaṃ—dānakathaṃ sīlakathaṃ saggakathaṃ; "
msgstr "a talk on giving, ethical conduct, and heaven. "

msgctxt "dn5:29.3"
msgid "kāmānaṃ ādīnavaṃ okāraṃ saṅkilesaṃ nekkhamme ānisaṃsaṃ pakāsesi. "
msgstr "He explained the drawbacks of sensual pleasures, so sordid and corrupt, and the benefit of renunciation. "

msgctxt "dn5:29.4"
msgid "Yadā bhagavā aññāsi kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ kallacittaṃ muducittaṃ vinīvaraṇacittaṃ udaggacittaṃ pasannacittaṃ, atha yā buddhānaṃ sāmukkaṃsikā dhammadesanā, taṃ pakāsesi—"
msgstr "And when he knew that Kūṭadanta’s mind was ready, pliable, rid of hindrances, joyful, and confident he explained the special teaching of the Buddhas: "

msgctxt "dn5:29.5"
msgid "dukkhaṃ samudayaṃ nirodhaṃ maggaṃ. "
msgstr "suffering, its origin, its cessation, and the path. "

msgctxt "dn5:29.6"
msgid "Seyyathāpi nāma suddhaṃ vatthaṃ apagatakāḷakaṃ sammadeva rajanaṃ paṭiggaṇheyya; "
msgstr "Just as a clean cloth rid of stains would properly absorb dye, "

msgctxt "dn5:29.7"
msgid "evameva kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa tasmiññeva āsane virajaṃ vītamalaṃ dhammacakkhuṃ udapādi: "
msgstr "in that very seat the stainless, immaculate vision of the Dhamma arose in the brahmin Kūṭadanta: "

msgctxt "dn5:29.8"
msgid "“yaṃ kiñci samudayadhammaṃ sabbaṃ taṃ nirodhadhamman”ti. "
msgstr "“Everything that has a beginning has an end.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-cs30, sc100
msgctxt "dn5:30.1"
msgid "Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo diṭṭhadhammo pattadhammo viditadhammo pariyogāḷhadhammo tiṇṇavicikiccho vigatakathaṅkatho vesārajjappatto aparappaccayo satthusāsane bhagavantaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then Kūṭadanta saw, attained, understood, and fathomed the Dhamma. He went beyond doubt, got rid of indecision, and became self-assured and independent of others regarding the Teacher’s instructions. He said to the Buddha, "

msgctxt "dn5:30.2"
msgid "“adhivāsetu me bhavaṃ gotamo svātanāya bhattaṃ saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghenā”ti. "
msgstr "“Would Master Gotama together with the mendicant Saṅgha please accept tomorrow’s meal from me?” "

msgctxt "dn5:30.3"
msgid "Adhivāsesi bhagavā tuṇhībhāvena. "
msgstr "The Buddha consented in silence. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc101
msgctxt "dn5:30.4"
msgid "Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavato adhivāsanaṃ viditvā uṭṭhāyāsanā bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā padakkhiṇaṃ katvā pakkāmi. "
msgstr "Then, knowing that the Buddha had consented, Kūṭadanta got up from his seat, bowed, and respectfully circled the Buddha, keeping him on his right, before leaving. "

msgctxt "dn5:30.5"
msgid "Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo tassā rattiyā accayena sake yaññavāṭe paṇītaṃ khādanīyaṃ bhojanīyaṃ paṭiyādāpetvā bhagavato kālaṃ ārocāpesi: "
msgstr "And when the night had passed Kūṭadanta had a variety of delicious foods prepared in his own home. Then he had the Buddha informed of the time, saying, "

msgctxt "dn5:30.6"
msgid "“kālo, bho gotama; niṭṭhitaṃ bhattan”ti. "
msgstr "“It’s time, Master Gotama, the meal is ready.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc102
msgctxt "dn5:30.7"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā pubbaṇhasamayaṃ nivāsetvā pattacīvaramādāya saddhiṃ bhikkhusaṅghena yena kūṭadantassa brāhmaṇassa yaññavāṭo tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha robed up in the morning and, taking his bowl and robe, went to the home of Kūṭadanta together with the mendicant Saṅgha, where he sat on the seat spread out. "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: pts-vp-pli1.149, sc103
msgctxt "dn5:30.8"
msgid "Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo buddhappamukhaṃ bhikkhusaṅghaṃ paṇītena khādanīyena bhojanīyena sahatthā santappesi sampavāresi. "
msgstr "Then Kūṭadanta served and satisfied the mendicant Saṅgha headed by the Buddha with his own hands with a variety of delicious foods. "

msgctxt "dn5:30.9"
msgid "Atha kho kūṭadanto brāhmaṇo bhagavantaṃ bhuttāviṃ onītapattapāṇiṃ aññataraṃ nīcaṃ āsanaṃ gahetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi. "
msgstr "When the Buddha had eaten and washed his hand and bowl, Kūṭadanta took a low seat and sat to one side. "

msgctxt "dn5:30.10"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinnaṃ kho kūṭadantaṃ brāhmaṇaṃ bhagavā dhammiyā kathāya sandassetvā samādapetvā samuttejetvā sampahaṃsetvā uṭṭhāyāsanā pakkāmīti. "
msgstr "Then the Buddha educated, encouraged, fired up, and inspired him with a Dhamma talk, after which he got up from his seat and left. "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsutta">
msgctxt "dn5:30.11"
msgid "Kūṭadantasuttaṃ niṭṭhitaṃ pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

